# Sirocco access-audit config (FindMeAccess-compatible).
# Restricts the -AccessAudit matrix to just these entries.
# Each line under a section may be a built-in NAME or a raw value
# (resource URL / client GUID / user-agent string). Unknown values are
# treated as custom entries. Omit a section to use all built-ins for it.
#
# Usage:
#   .\Sirocco.ps1 ... -AccessAudit -AuditConfig .\audit.conf

[resources]
Azure Graph API
Microsoft Graph API
Azure Management API
Outlook

[clients]
Microsoft Azure PowerShell
Microsoft Azure CLI
Microsoft Office
Microsoft Authentication Broker

[user_agents]
Windows 10 Chrome
Android Chrome
iPhone Safari
